    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六名少年少女在不知不觉间误入的「错综杂音城」是过去的心灵创伤化作“杂音”显现而出的迷宫。与“杂音”正面交锋，治愈心灵创伤，逃离这座迷宫都市吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/4fd0940de886d8d3843475e0e27cb28b.poster.avif?t=1761724281\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/4fd0940de886d8d3843475e0e27cb28b.webm?t=1761724281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/4fd0940de886d8d3843475e0e27cb28b.mp4?t=1761724281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■体验版公开中！此前的试玩版可以游玩登场角色之一“阳缘”篇的部分剧情，而本次更新后，将新增正式版第1、2章的部分内容。此外，还将追加3种解谜、探索环节，大幅增强游戏内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解谜推进剧情，而剧情又是解谜的关键——请借此机会充分体验本作特有的新型ADV玩法吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>存档数据无法继承到正式版。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/fca83be4458a4965f9544d4985f729c9.avif?t=1761724281\" width=300 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 关于直播</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版全部内容都可直播！欢迎在社交媒体上分享感想！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意避免剧透！请使用 <strong><u>#残音系少年少女</u></strong> 进行发布！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有关详细的直播指南，请查看官方网站！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/42bff672f7b8177cdee0975d06123c86.poster.avif?t=1761724281\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/42bff672f7b8177cdee0975d06123c86.webm?t=1761724281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/42bff672f7b8177cdee0975d06123c86.mp4?t=1761724281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■探索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷宫都市「错综杂音城」乍看之下像是普通的日本城市，却拥有着与日常生活严重脱轨的诡异形态。请在探索中获取「杂音碎片」，以此为线索唤醒少年少女们的记忆吧。掌握他们的心灵创伤将使迷宫的形态发生变化，并逐渐展露出隐藏其后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/44236ea7b876ce3127d4696eb0dccde8.poster.avif?t=1761724281\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/44236ea7b876ce3127d4696eb0dccde8.webm?t=1761724281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185370/extras/44236ea7b876ce3127d4696eb0dccde8.mp4?t=1761724281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■杂音</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所谓杂音，既是人们不愿去回想的记忆被展露在外界的物理形态。通过将探索中获取的「杂音碎片」进行拼合，可以唤醒少年少女们遗失的记忆——心灵创伤。这些心灵创伤当中包含他们曾经遭遇的事件与回忆，其中隐藏着揭开谜团的线索甚至答案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请聆听她的杂音，揭露所有谜题吧！！好评公开中！</strong></p>",
